{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461630/extras/store_insert.png?t=1734829071\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Overview</h2><br>Magic Potion Millionaire is a side-scrolling action game focused on money-making.<br>Enter the dungeon to gather materials, make potions, and sell them to make profit!<br><br>Gold is everything here. Pastel can buy various things to upgrade herself.<br>Become stronger, challenge harder dungeons, make more gold...<br>until your competitor surrenders.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1. Enter the dungeon for materials!<br>Enter and conquer procedurally generated dungeons with melee attacks, various ranged attacks and magic potions.<br>You can create potions with the materials you find from enemies in the dungeon. <br>Potions are not only limited to healing drinks, and you can make other kinds such as explosive potions (bombs).<br><br></li><li>2. Brew potions to make money!<br>Using the materials you gather in the dungeon, you can make potions the clients will order.<br>Your potion shop will have many orders to fulfill, and much money to make.<br><br></li><li>3. Buy stuff to become stronger!<br>There are many uses for gold you have earned.<br>Buy equipments to improve your stats, buy recipes for more potions, find new dungeons to explore, and so on.<br>They will sure help you make more money!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><br>In a forest on the outskirts of the town, there's a magic potion shop.<br>Its owner Pastel, has a thriving business as there were no rivals around. One day she said...<br>&quot;Everything's going so well! I love being in this business, with no other game in town!&quot;<br><br>A strange-looking customer heard that, and told her...<br>&quot;That sounds like you're looking for a competitor, aren't you?&quot;<br><br>... One month later.<br>A new magic potion shop has opened in the town, and it took all the customers Pastel had.<br>Pastel reflects on her arrogance and decides to reopen her shop....","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Witch's Scissors","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/a2673eea5af95f2fba530741ef7a50a595cb3fc9.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Shortcut","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/5d98081b27f1138084b3b1ef5a51bc974f52f5f7.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Prayer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/065591c3b94ec5531e15c9e25a5062bd8ae73c25.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Homerun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/ebb9f6aa9eff1f2a008f0dc61b358f62eabe5d4c.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Delight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/9b5b52b034f0efa0f35cda29320e1be8f2b97cf9.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Safety Plan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/337ec59a0aa4364a14830f33592fc0e2923afa8d.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Pendant","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/5875d75b1d282aa419281bbb342963eeee053cbc.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Iron Hammer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/e513007bb843667bcfd490ef43ac92e4c95d205d.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Excitement","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/64a401e9e4d2813475b6a92523959a82eb8e04d7.jpg"},{"name":"Witch's Punishment","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1461630/b6dd56076ad7835c85e188095db6ff34b73f27f5.jpg"}],"total":40},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461630/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734829071","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1461630/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734829071","capsule_image":"https: